-- Brown & Brown Names Case as Environmental Liability Group Leader
-- B y   M e g a n   H i c k e y
-- 2013-06-18T21:02:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-18/brown-brown-names-case-as-environmental-liability-group-leader.html
Brown & Brown Inc., the family run
insurance intermediary, named Jeffrey B. Case as environmental
liability practice group leader of the wholesale brokerage
division.  “We expect the sales leadership skills and creativity Jeff
brings to this endeavor to improve our operations,” Anthony Strianese, regional president, said today in a statement from
the  Daytona Beach , Florida-based broker.  To contact the reporter on this story:
